song.title: The 'Click' Cafe
song.info:
Hi everyone! I am back, and I got a new song I made in just 4 hours! I hope you enjoy this little peice, it sounds quite odd does it not? I like it a lot, and I dedicate it to all the clickers out there I know! The tune was supposed to be a cafe tune for a game, but it didn't quite sound like it, and I said "This reminds me of the Click Cafe" and there! Is my title. Hope you enjoyed the song everyone,
-Nobuyuki
